  <main id="main" class="container" role="main">
    <h1>Service Workers</h1>
    <div class="card">
      <p>Service workers are event-driven scripts that run in the background. They intercept network requests, manage caches, and enable offline-first experiences.</p>
      <h2>Lifecycle</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>install</strong> — good place to pre-cache critical assets.</li>
        <li><strong>activate</strong> — clear old caches, take control.</li>
        <li><strong>fetch</strong> — respond with cache/network based on strategy.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </main>

