  <main id="main" class="container" role="main">
    <h1>Key Concepts (5–7)</h1>
    <div class="grid cols-2">
      <section class="card"><h2>Offline-first</h2><p>Serve cached content when the network is slow or unavailable.</p></section>
      <section class="card"><h2>Precache vs Runtime</h2><p>Precache app shell on install; runtime cache specific requests later.</p></section>
      <section class="card"><h2>Installability</h2><p>Valid manifest + served over HTTPS + service worker = install prompts.</p></section>
      <section class="card"><h2>PWAs on iOS</h2><p>Use Apple meta tags for home-screen behavior; support partial features.</p></section>
      <section class="card"><h2>Caching Strategies</h2><p>Stale-while-revalidate, cache-first, network-first—pick per route.</p></section>
      <section class="card"><h2>App Shell</h2><p>Cache your UI shell so navigations feel instant.</p></section>
    </div>
  </main>

